            <code class="function">glLoadIdentity</code> replaces the current matrix with the identity matrix.
            It is semantically equivalent to calling <span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glLoadMatrix</span></span>
            with the identity matrix
        </p><p>
        </p><p>
